### ===============================
### TEST API COMMENTI - StreetCats
### ===============================

### Dettaglio singolo commento
GET http://localhost:3000/comments/1

###

### Modifica commento (richiede autenticazione + owner/admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/comments/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TEST_TOKEN}}

{
  "text": "Testo del commento modificato"
}

###

### Elimina commento (richiede autenticazione + owner/admin)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TEST_TOKEN}}

###

### Lista commenti di un utente
GET http://localhost:3000/users/mario@example.com/comments
